00:14:00,704 --> 00:14:03,165
Who's the Messiah
of Silence?

248
00:14:03,165 --> 00:14:06,752
She is the final Guardian,
the one who must not be

249
00:14:06,752 --> 00:14:08,295
allowed to awaken.

250
00:14:08,295 --> 00:14:09,838
She will appear at the
moment the world is

251
00:14:09,838 --> 00:14:12,799
about to be destroyed
and lead us all to

252
00:14:12,799 --> 00:14:15,218
death and nothingness.

253
00:14:15,927 --> 00:14:17,345
[gasp]

254
00:14:20,932 --> 00:14:22,726
This Messiah of Silence...

255
00:14:22,726 --> 00:14:24,019
Who is exactly is she?

256
00:14:24,019 --> 00:14:25,062
Don't worry about that.

257
00:14:25,062 --> 00:14:28,356
She will show her
true self very soon.

258
00:14:29,941 --> 00:14:30,442
[gasp]

259
00:14:30,442 --> 00:14:32,402
[fright screams and shouts]

260
00:14:32,944 --> 00:14:37,199
[scared chatter]

261
00:14:42,037 --> 00:14:45,916
[screechy laughter]

262
00:14:46,374 --> 00:14:48,168
I'm U Choten!

263
00:14:48,168 --> 00:14:51,922
And I'm here to help
you wish upon a star!

264
00:14:51,963 --> 00:14:53,090
Hah!

265
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:55,383
[fright yell]

266
00:15:00,931 --> 00:15:03,934
Time to make
a wish. Ready?!

267
00:15:05,936 --> 00:15:08,021
Everyone! Take cover!

268
00:15:09,940 --> 00:15:11,733
[chuckles]

269
00:15:12,067 --> 00:15:16,196
Agh! No! Stay away!

270
00:15:16,363 --> 00:15:17,948
[chuckles]

271
00:15:17,948 --> 00:15:19,950
Good work, U Choten!

272
00:15:19,950 --> 00:15:21,952
[laugh]

273
00:15:21,952 --> 00:15:24,913
Yes, it certainly
was! I rock.

274
00:15:24,913 --> 00:15:26,206
[sigh] U Choten, don't worry

275
00:15:26,206 --> 00:15:27,749
