Mr. Harris' pure heart.

277
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:32,754
U Choten!

278
00:15:32,754 --> 00:15:33,964
But before she does...

279
00:15:33,964 --> 00:15:35,298
Can I have your autograph?

280
00:15:35,298 --> 00:15:37,300
[angry scream]

281
00:15:37,926 --> 00:15:39,010
Guess not...

282
00:15:39,094 --> 00:15:41,930
