00:15:44,432 --> 00:15:48,186
Charm Buster!

284
00:15:48,937 --> 00:15:50,438
[screams]

285
00:15:51,940 --> 00:15:54,901
Don't make a sound.
Let's hide here.

286
00:15:54,901 --> 00:15:56,194
Okay...

287
00:15:56,194 --> 00:15:58,530
Oh no! Hotaru!

288
00:15:59,239 --> 00:16:02,993
I'll be okay. It's
just the usual attack.

289
00:16:02,993 --> 00:16:03,660
It'll be over soon.

290
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:07,289
That means you have to go
to the hospital! Hang on!

291
00:16:07,289 --> 00:16:09,249
I gotta transform...

292
00:16:09,457 --> 00:16:10,208
Not yet.

293
00:16:10,208 --> 00:16:12,836
Uranus! Hold on, and let's
see what happens.

294
00:16:12,836 --> 00:16:14,546
I'm not sure we
have the time!

295
00:16:14,546 --> 00:16:15,881
Hold it right
there, Daimon!

296
00:16:15,881 --> 00:16:17,924
A planetarium's a
place for dreams!

297
00:16:17,924 --> 00:16:20,010
A place where stars
shine bright!

298
00:16:20,010 --> 00:16:21,928
A place of magical
discovery!

299
00:16:21,928 --> 00:16:24,723
Anyone who ruins this
dream‐filled place...

300
00:16:24,723 --> 00:16:27,684
Will have to deal with
the Sailor Guardians!

301
00:16:27,684 --> 00:16:32,230
And now, in the name of the
Moon, we'll punish you!

302
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:34,191
Well, I guess nothing we
could have said was

303
00:16:34,191 --> 00:16:37,152
going to keep those
girls from transforming.

304
00:16:37,152 --> 00:16:40,530
Right. Why do you girls always
have to get in my way?!

305
00:16:40,572 --> 00:16:41,656
U Choten!

306
00:16:41,656 --> 00:16:43,533
What?!That pure heart
can wait a moment.

307
00:16:43,533 --> 00:16:46,036
Get rid of these
Sailor Clowns first!

308
00:16:46,036 --> 00:16:47,120
Fine!

309
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,955
Don't disappoint me now.

310
00:16:48,955 --> 00:16:49,915
Yes, ma'am!

311
00:16:49,915 --> 00:16:52,334
Are you all ready
to have some fun?

312
00:16:52,334 --> 00:16:53,460
[affirmative grunt]

313
00:16:53,460 --> 00:16:57,339
Well, here we go!
Wish upon a star!

314
00:16:57,923 --> 00:16:58,965
[screams]

315
00:16:59,925 --> 00:17:02,135
That's it! Keep wishing!

316
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:04,888
[yells]

317
00:17:04,930 --> 00:17:07,849
[nasty laugh] U Choten!

318
00:17:07,849 --> 00:17:10,644
Cast your eyes up
to the night sky!

319
00:17:13,813 --> 00:17:14,981
Hotaru, hang in there!

320
00:17:14,981 --> 00:17:17,192
This isn't good.
We're cornered here.

321
00:17:17,192 --> 00:17:18,526
We have to do something!

322
00:17:18,526 --> 00:17:21,947
Not heavenly enough for
you? Alright, then‐‐‐

323
00:17:21,947 --> 00:17:23,240
[scream of pain]

324
00:17:23,949 --> 00:17:25,533
What the‐?

325
00:17:25,867 --> 00:17:28,912
That's as far as you go,
Daimon. No evil star shall

326
00:17:28,912 --> 00:17:31,289
harm the innocent,
under my watch!

327
00:17:31,289 --> 00:17:34,376
Your glow is about to fade!

328
00:17:34,459 --> 00:17:38,797
[chuckles]You're wrong, my glow
is stronger than you think!

329
00:17:38,922 --> 00:17:39,965
It's time!

330
00:17:39,965 --> 00:17:41,550
Make a wish!

331
00:17:42,133 --> 00:17:43,385
Ready?

332
00:17:44,177 --> 00:17:44,928
Hah!

333
00:17:45,345 --> 00:17:46,763
Stay clear, everyone!

334
00:17:46,763 --> 00:17:49,182
Did Tuxedo Mask just
make things much worse?

335
00:17:49,182 --> 00:17:50,183
Venus, get down!

336
00:17:50,183 --> 00:17:53,436
Hotaru! You have
to stay down!

337
00:17:54,479 --> 00:17:56,773
[gasp]

338
00:18:03,405 --> 00:18:05,073
[gasp] It's her!

339
00:18:05,073 --> 00:18:06,199
Hotaru?

340
00:18:07,951 --> 00:18:08,910
What's...

341
00:18:08,910 --> 00:18:10,870
...Going on?!

342
00:18:11,121 --> 00:18:12,747
That symbol!

343
00:18:12,914 --> 00:18:14,916
So Hotaru is...

344
00:18:14,916 --> 00:18:17,210
A Sailor Guardian?

345
00:18:19,588 --> 00:18:21,548
What's she doing?

346
00:18:24,175 --> 00:18:24,926
Agh! What?

347
00:18:24,926 --> 00:18:29,014
