I can't move!

348
00:18:29,014 --> 00:18:31,558
Sailor Moon,
now's your chance!

349
00:18:33,310 --> 00:18:37,939
Crisis Make Up!

350
00:19:05,425 --> 00:19:13,850
Rainbow Moon Heartache!

351
00:19:21,316 --> 00:19:24,235
[gasp] [scream]

352
