Love Lovely!

353
00:19:44,923 --> 00:19:48,218
World Shaking!

354
00:19:49,761 --> 00:19:50,929
[gasp]

355
00:19:54,683 --> 00:19:58,645
Deep Submerge!

356
00:20:01,231 --> 00:20:03,566
