368
00:20:46,651 --> 00:20:49,195
So, move! You have absolutely no
idea how frightening

369
00:20:49,195 --> 00:20:50,155
the Silence will be!

370
00:20:50,155 --> 00:20:52,282
Unless we're able
to kill that girl,

371
00:20:52,282 --> 00:20:52,991
Saturn will awaken!

372
00:20:52,991 --> 00:20:55,577
And if that happens,
it will mean the end of

373
00:20:55,577 --> 00:20:57,245
life as you know it!
We understand,

374
00:20:57,287 --> 00:20:58,913
but we can't let you
kill this girl!

375
00:20:58,913 --> 00:21:01,750
Listen to us! Even if
Hotaru is the Guardian of

376
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:03,793
Destruction, that doesn't
give you the right to

377
00:21:03,793 --> 00:21:05,920
kill her! She's still
just a little girl!

378
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:09,048
What you're talking about
doing is horrible and cruel!

379
00:21:09,048 --> 00:21:10,925
There has to be another way!

380
00:21:10,925 --> 00:21:12,969
We thought that's what
